definitions.meaning: 不是；没有（am not, is not, are not等的缩写形式，常用于口语）

ain’t.memory_method: 他ain’t 准备好了。(He ain’t ready.)

be about to.memory_method: 火车be about to出发了，我们快上车。(The train is about to depart. Let's get on quickly.)

be into.memory_method: 她很be into绘画，一有空就去画画。(She is really into painting and goes to paint whenever she has time.)

beat sb to it.memory_method: 我正打算去买最后一张票，结果他beat me to it。(I was about to buy the last ticket, but he beat me to it.)

fall out.memory_method: 他们曾经是好朋友，但因为一点小事fall out了。(They were good friends once, but they fell out because of a small thing.)

feel...so hard.memory_method: 我对他的经历feel this so hard，因为我也有过类似的遭遇。(I feel his experience so hard because I've had similar experiences.)

get dates.memory_method: 他最近运气真好，总能get dates。(He's been really lucky recently and can always get dates.)

definitions.meaning: 笑死（laugh my ass off的缩写，用于表示非常好笑）

lmao.memory_method: 他刚刚讲的笑话太逗了，lmao。(The joke he just told was so funny, lmao.)

meme.memory_method: 这个meme在网上迅速传播开来。(This meme spread quickly on the Internet.)

show off.memory_method: 他总是喜欢show off他的新玩具。(He always likes to show off his new toys.)

definitions.meaning: （在手机屏幕上）滑动选择（如在约会软件上滑动选择感兴趣的人）

swipe on.memory_method: 你需要在这个应用上swipe on来选择你喜欢的商品。(You need to swipe on this app to choose the products you like.)
